sequenceDiagram
    participant UI as Modern Migration UI
    participant GW as API Gateway
    participant ORCH as Migration Orchestrator
    participant MS_CONN as Microsoft Connector
    participant MAP as Data Mapping Service
    participant STAGE as Staging Service
    participant DB as Migration Database
    participant MP as Marketplace APIs

    Note over UI,MP: Migration Process Flow

    UI->>GW: Initiate Migration Process
    GW->>ORCH: Route Migration Request
    
    ORCH->>MS_CONN: Request Tenant Validation
    MS_CONN->>MS_CONN: Validate Microsoft Tenant
    MS_CONN-->>ORCH: Tenant Validation Result
    
    alt Tenant Valid
        ORCH->>MS_CONN: Retrieve Subscription Data
        MS_CONN->>MS_CONN: Fetch from Microsoft APIs
        MS_CONN-->>ORCH: Raw Subscription Data
        
        ORCH->>MAP: Process Data Mapping
        MAP->>MAP: Apply Field Mappings
        MAP->>MAP: Transform Data Format
        MAP-->>ORCH: Mapped Data
        
        ORCH->>STAGE: Stage Data for Processing
        STAGE->>STAGE: Apply Bulk Markups
        STAGE->>STAGE: Prepare for Marketplace
        STAGE->>DB: Store Staged Data
        STAGE-->>ORCH: Staging Complete
        
        ORCH->>MP: Create Products/Invoices
        MP->>MP: Generate Marketplace Objects
        MP-->>ORCH: Creation Success
        
        ORCH->>DB: Update Migration Status
        ORCH-->>GW: Migration Complete
        GW-->>UI: Success Response
        
    else Tenant Invalid
        ORCH->>DB: Log Validation Failure
        ORCH-->>GW: Error Response
        GW-->>UI: Error Message
    end

    Note over UI,MP: Data Flow Responsibilities<br/>• Connectors: Data Retrieval & Validation<br/>• Mapping: Data Transformation<br/>• Staging: Bulk Operations & Markups<br/>• Orchestrator: Process Management<br/>• Migration Team: Backend Data Management

